According to estimates in various studies, 70-70% of men who have sexual relations with other men eventually marry women because of the conservative values of the country.
In many cases, the disease spreads in these relationships due to inadequate sexual protection.
Since 2003, the Chinese government has been providing universal access to HIV medicines as part of a program to solve the problem.
